                <h1>Recess reviews: HBO&#039;s &#039;Big Little Lies&#039; explores the complexities of the female experience </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/507ab2ab-b3d7-40f5-be8a-0d451a5e54ef.sized-1000x1000.png?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;&#x201C;Big&#x20;Little&#x20;Lies&#x201D;&#x20;manages&#x20;to&#x20;be&#x20;genuine&#x20;without&#x20;becoming&#x20;boring,&#x20;combining&#x20;genuine&#x20;characters&#x20;with&#x20;a&#x20;murder&#x20;mystery.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>“Big Little Lies” manages to be genuine without becoming boring, combining genuine characters with a murder mystery.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/christy-kuesel">Christy Kuesel </a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">April 26, 2017 | 12:00am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2017/04/bllreview" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2017/04/bllreview&amp;text=Recess reviews: HBO&#039;s &#039;Big Little Lies&#039; explores the complexities of the female experience " target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="twitter" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a></li>
                                                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="mailto:?subject=Recess%20reviews%3A%20HBO%27s%20%27Big%20Little%20Lies%27%20explores%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20female%20experience%20%20|%20The%20Chronicle&amp;message=Check%20out%20this%20article%20from%20The%20Chronicle%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dukechronicle.com%2Farticle%2F2017%2F04%2Fbllreview" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="email" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i></a></li>
